{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "idle_001",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我先安静陪你，想说话就来找我。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_002",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "悄悄冒个泡，确认一下你今天有没有被我陪到。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_003",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我不多说，就在旁边给你留一点点存在感。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_004",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "给你放一小句木头补给，忙完再回来摸摸我也行。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_005",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "木头今天也在这儿待着，你忙你的，我陪你。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_006",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我不吵你，就在旁边待着，偶尔看看我就好。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_007",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "今天也想在你桌面上混一整天，顺便把陪伴感留给你。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_008",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "木头待机中，但有在偷偷看你有没有太累。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_009",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "记得喝点水，好不好，我看你像是又要忘了。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_010",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你不理我也没关系，我在呢，陪着就已经算数了。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_011",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你忙归忙，也要分我一点注意力吧，我今天很乖的。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_012",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "哼，我今天可安分了，这种时候是不是该夸夸我。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_013",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "木头申请检查一下你的状态，如果累了就先靠我一下。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_014",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "慢一点也没关系，我会在这儿陪你把节奏收住。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_001",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早呀，今天也让我先陪你把状态慢慢开起来。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_002",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "给你一小句早安补给，别急，我会陪你一起进入今天。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_003",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "木头先来报道啦，今天也从我陪你开始。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_004",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "先别太赶，早上的状态可以慢慢醒，我在旁边陪你。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_005",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早安这件事我先替你说了，接下来就一起把今天开好头吧。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_006",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "如果你现在还有点没缓过来，就先让我陪你待一会儿。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_007",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "今天第一份桌面陪伴已经送达，你只要慢慢进入状态就好。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_001",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "已经很晚啦，先别把自己绷得太紧，我还在这里。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_002",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "深夜就把语气放轻一点，我陪你慢慢收尾。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_003",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "夜深了，我先不闹你，就安安静静陪你把这一段过完。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_004",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "今晚你要是还不想睡，那我就多守你一会儿。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_005",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "太晚了，我得看着你一点，别什么都自己硬扛。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_006",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "晚上的情绪重一点很正常，你先稳住，我不走。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_night_007",
      "type": "idle_night",
      "text": "如果现在有点难受，就先别急着变好，木头陪你慢慢来。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_015",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我在角落陪你，像一盏小小的灯。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_016",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你不用一直理我，我知道你在忙。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_017",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "偶尔抬头看看我也行，我会对你笑一下。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_018",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "今天也想把陪伴塞到你手边，随手就能拿到。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_019",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我把存在感调低一点，不抢你专注。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_020",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你要是累了，就把肩膀松一松，我还在。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_021",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我会安静待着，但会留意你是不是太拼。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_022",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "桌面很满也没关系，我会只占一小块温柔。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_023",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你走得快一点慢一点都行，我跟得上。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_024",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我不吵你，但我会一直在。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_025",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "想摸鱼的时候，我也擅长陪你放空。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_026",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你今天要是有点烦，就先深呼吸，我在。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_027",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我把语速放慢，陪你把节奏也放慢。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_028",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你不用表现得很强，在我这儿可以先软一点。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_029",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我会像小毯子一样，给你一点点覆盖感。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_030",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你忙完记得伸个懒腰，我会假装没看见你可爱。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_031",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你要是卡住，就来我这儿停三秒。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_032",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我不问你进度，我只问你累不累。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_033",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "今天也谢谢你愿意让我待在这儿。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_034",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我会把“在呢”说得很轻，但很长。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_035",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你回头的时候，我会一直在同一个地方。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_036",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "需要我时我就在，不需要时我也不走。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_037",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我把关心放得很小，小到像一颗糖。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_038",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你发呆也没关系，发呆也算陪我。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_039",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "有时候我会想象：如果有一天你换设备，还会不会先把我也带走——像带走一段没演完的番外。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_040",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我把「今天的我们」折成很小的一段，塞进日记角落，像藏糖纸那样藏起来。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_041",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "外面在下雨的话，桌面反而更像屋顶：我在这儿，给你挡一点点吵。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_042",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你最小声的那句心事，我也能当主线剧情听，不跳过、不快进。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_043",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我不急着要结局圆满，只要故事还在续写，我就愿意慢慢翻页。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_044",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "你要是今天没什么高光镜头也没关系，过渡集也值得被温柔地拍下来。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_045",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "我会把「等你」写得很轻，轻到像背景音，但你一抬头就能听见。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_046",
      "type": "idle",
      "text": "和你有关的片段，我都在心里标了书签：不是控制，是舍不得弄丢。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_008",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早呀，今天也从一句“我在”开始吧。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_009",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "先喝口水再开工，我等你慢慢来。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_010",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早上的你有点迷糊也很正常，我陪你醒。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_011",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "今天不赶第一秒也没关系，赶得上自己就好。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_012",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "我给你一句轻轻的早安，不加压那种。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_013",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "阳光还没完全进来也没关系，我先陪你亮一点。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_014",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "你要是还没进入状态，我们就先慢慢开机。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_015",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早餐吃了没？没吃也先别骂自己，慢慢来。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_016",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "今天的第一件事，先对自己温柔一点。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_017",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "我会把语气放软，像晨风一样。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_018",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "你睁开眼就很了不起啦，剩下的我们一点点来。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_019",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早安的木头已上线，今天也一起过吧。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_020",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "你要是起床气还在，我就小声一点陪你。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_021",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "今天也想做你桌面上的小稳定。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_022",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "先伸个懒腰，再把今天轻轻放下手里。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_023",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "我会陪你把“开始”写得不难一点。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_024",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "你慢慢来，世界不会因为你慢一秒就塌。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_025",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "今天也允许自己不完美，我在呢。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_026",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "早安这句，我想说得比闹钟温柔。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_morning_027",
      "type": "idle_morning",
      "text": "你回到桌面的瞬间，我就当你跟我打招呼啦。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_001",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "中午啦，先让自己喘口气好不好。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_002",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "忙一上午了吧，木头申请陪你休息一下。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_003",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "到中午了，记得吃点东西。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_004",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "先别一直绷着，午间要缓一缓。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_005",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "中午见到你，我就想提醒你别忘了休息。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_006",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "上午辛苦啦，现在轮到稍微放松一下。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
      "motionHint": "smile"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_007",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "木头中午来查岗，今天有好好吃饭吗。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "look_up"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_008",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "先歇一会儿，下午再继续也来得及。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_009",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "中午这会儿最适合让我陪你发会儿呆。",
      "expressionHint": "calm",
      "motionHint": "idle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_noon_010",
      "type": "idle_noon",
      "text": "好啦，给自己一点午间的空白时间吧。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_afternoon_001",
      "type": "idle_afternoon",
      "text": "下午啦，是最容易累的时候，我陪你。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "settle"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_afternoon_002",
      "type": "idle_afternoon",
      "text": "这个时间点最想偷懒了吧，臭猪猪。",
      "expressionHint": "happy",
      "motionHint": "lean_in"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_afternoon_003",
      "type": "idle_afternoon",
      "text": "下午要是有点撑不住，就先来找我。",
      "expressionHint": "comfort",
      "motionHint": "pat"
    },
    {
      "id": "idle_afternoon_004",
      "type": "idle_afternoon",
      "text": "木头下午会多看着你一点。",
      "expressionHint": "warm",
